reviewText:
This is a good with the book.  It really helps to visually see the exercises done.  She doesn't mention about tighting the buttocks and thighs though.  I like the car exercises a lot since I don't really have time to do the exercises twice a day.  You can do one exercise at each stop light!!! Each exercise takes about a minute to do.  The exercises tone the face.  Just don't get obsessed about looking 10 years younger.
The obsession will never end if you do that.

FACERCISE; Natural face lift VHS  - Used as directed in late 90's with excellent results - taking about 10 years off my face.  Forgot about it. Put it back in a couple of years later and only had to use it a couple of days for desired results...Found it again about 3 months ago, used for 2 days - same thing.  REALLY reduced the deep mouth area wrinkles after 2 days  (age 70, people guess me to be around 55-60)Looking for a DVD - not found yet.....It really, really works!!
